Did you mean:
```suggestion
/-- In a non-trivial series `p`, the last element of `p.eraseLast` is related to `p.last` -/
```
Yes, not sure how that got capitalized.
I think we adopted the policy that hypotheses should be of the form x \ne 0, not 0 < x

Thanks to `omega`, no changes needed in the proof nor its use in my project. Nice.
```suggestion
lemma eraseLast_last_rel_last (p : RelSeries r) (h : p.length ≠ 0) :
```
